Purchasing Superintendent - Tuban - PT Holcim Indonesia Tbk
Purchasing Superintendent - Tuban  -
Purchasing Superintendent - Tuban
Responsibilities
Scope of works:                     As Purchasing Superintendent, the incumbent will be responsible to manage the systematic process of deciding what, when and how much to purchase and also to ensure that what is required by end user is received on time in the quality specified. The task will be covering, but not limited to:Negotiate and prepare series of options to purchase goods/ services at the best conditions with the aim reducing total Cost of OwnershipSelect the vendor, considering the end user recommendation and the vendor performanceExecute a procurement process based on theprocurement policy and procedureEnsure that the purchasing KPI (key Performance Indicator) on the PO processing time and on time delivery are achieved and aligned with the procurement policy & procedureDevelope and coach buyers and senior buyers through their individual development program   Education : Bachelor Degree from reputable university, degree in Engineering (Industrial, Mechanical or Electrical) is preferableExperience : 5 years holding the similar position in any multinational manufacturing company (with 2 years experience as supervisor)Computer literacy : Microsoft officeLanguage : Good command in English oral and writtenOther qualification / skills : Excellent in leadership and coaching skillStrong analytical and problem solving skillExcellent negotiation skillGood communication interpersonal skillAbility to work both independently and in a team environmentHave good technical skill in cement industry is preferable
